<td style="width: 8.719616%; height: 96px;">Example</td>
<td style="width: 46.823064%; height: 96px;">Describing the components and workings of a car engine, including pistons, crankshaft, and fuel injection system.</td>
<td style="width: 44.457319%; height: 96px;"> Defining “CPU” as the central processing unit  of a computer, responsible for executing  instructions from software.</td>
</tr>
